data.description: Recently updated, split-level home, located in the heart of Conway! 3-bedrooms, 2-full bathrooms and an abundance of storage closets! Entertain all year round with your open floor plan and finished game room inside or get ready for Summer and host your next BBQ on your rear patio and flat, fenced-in backyard, which is perfect for relaxing! Brand new large TREX deck. Updated mechanicals. Minutes from RT 65, 51, Cranberry, shopping and so much more! Walking distance to the Ed Gratty park, basketball courts and baseball fields!
